---
import { Search, MapPin, Target, Smartphone, BarChart3, ArrowRight } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section class="py-20 bg-white" id="capabilities">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-[#0a0a0a] mb-6 tracking-tight">
        A <span class="text-gradient">Full-Stack Growth Ecosystem</span>.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600">
        We integrate four core disciplines to drive efficiency and volume. No silos, just a unified strategy for clinic growth.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <!-- Card 1: Search -->
      <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-100 hover:border-brand/20 transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-8">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-brand group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <Search className="w-7 h-7" />
          </div>
          <span class="text-slate-200 font-black text-6xl leading-none select-none group-hover:text-slate-200/80 transition-colors">01</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Search & Local Dominance (SEO)</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 italic">
            "Beyond basic keywords."
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            We engineer your digital presence to dominate "Near Me" searches and high-value treatment queries. We optimize your Google Business Profile and site architecture to capture patients actively looking for care.
        </p>
        <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">Includes: <span class="font-normal text-slate-600">Local SEO, Technical Audits, Content Strategy.</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: PPC -->
      <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-100 hover:border-brand/20 transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-8">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-brand group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <Target className="w-7 h-7" />
          </div>
          <span class="text-slate-200 font-black text-6xl leading-none select-none group-hover:text-slate-200/80 transition-colors">02</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Paid Media Acquisition (PPC)</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 italic">
            "Precision targeting, zero waste."
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            We run compliant Google & Social ad campaigns designed to lower your Cost Per Acquisition (CPA). We target high-intent patients, not just "clicks," ensuring your budget fills appointment slots.
        </p>
        <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">Includes: <span class="font-normal text-slate-600">Google Search Ads, Meta (FB/IG) Ads, Display Retargeting.</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

       <!-- Card 3: Web Dev -->
       <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-100 hover:border-brand/20 transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-8">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-brand group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <Smartphone className="w-7 h-7" />
          </div>
          <span class="text-slate-200 font-black text-6xl leading-none select-none group-hover:text-slate-200/80 transition-colors">03</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Medical Web Development</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 italic">
            "Built for conversion, not just aesthetics."
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            We deploy lightning-fast, mobile-first websites optimized for Google’s Core Web Vitals. Every page is structured to guide visitors toward the "Book Now" button while adhering to MOH guidelines.
        </p>
        <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">Includes: <span class="font-normal text-slate-600">Lamanify Site™, UX/UI Design, Speed Optimization.</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 4: Analytics -->
      <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[2rem] border border-slate-100 hover:border-brand/20 transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-8">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-brand group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
            <BarChart3 className="w-7 h-7" />
          </div>
          <span class="text-slate-200 font-black text-6xl leading-none select-none group-hover:text-slate-200/80 transition-colors">04</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Analytics & Attribution</h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6 italic">
            "Know exactly what works."
        </p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            We move beyond vanity metrics. Our custom dashboards track every lead source, phone call, and form submission, giving you total clarity on your Marketing ROI.
        </p>
        <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900">Includes: <span class="font-normal text-slate-600">Custom Dashboards, Call Tracking, CRM Integration.</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center">
        <a href="/services" class="inline-flex items-center text-brand font-bold hover:text-brand-dark transition-colors text-lg group">
            View Full Service Capabilities
            <ArrowRight className="w-5 h-5 ml-2 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" />
        </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
